videos.headline: Kamilla Cardoso puts up huge stat line as South Carolina remains undefeated
videos.description: Kamilla Cardoso gets her third double-double of the season to power South Carolina past South Dakota State.

tracking.trackingName: NCW_Highlight (Kamilla Cardoso puts up huge stat line as South Carolina remains undefeated) 2023/11/20 ESHEET

videos.headline: Johnson on Gamecocks' camaraderie, win over Jackrabbits
videos.description: After logging five steals and a career-high 16 points vs. South Dakota State, Raven Johnson hypes up No. 1 South Carolina's MiLaysia Fulwiley and Kamilla Cardoso.
